cpan6 - A tool to assist in creating and sharing CPAN modules

Available commands
  bootstrap config [opton]
  bootstrap man    [page]
  bump            [--force]
  bump      major [--force]
  bump      minor [--force]
  bump      patch [--force]
  depend    [--skip-install] <modules...>
  dist      [--force] [--verbose]
  help
  new       [--force] [--git] [--travis] [name]
  push      [--no-bump] <path>
  test
  touch     bin      <provide>
  touch     class    <provide>
  touch     resource <resource>
  touch     test     <test>
  touch     unit     <provide>
  upload    [--pause-id=<id>] [--pause-password=<password>] <dists...>
